## Conventions

- Use {{formatter}} for formatting (auto-runs on save via hook)
- TypeScript strict; no `any` escapes
- Imports: absolute via `@/` alias
- Tests colocated as `*.test.ts`

## Don't

- Don't edit `.env*` files (blocked by `permissions.deny`)
- Don't run `npm publish` (blocked)
- Don't commit `.claude/settings.local.json`

## Plan mode for unfamiliar areas

When working in unfamiliar parts of the codebase, prefer `claude --permission-mode plan` first.

## CI

PRs are auto-reviewed by `claude -p` in `.github/workflows/claude-review.yml`.
